on": ["GADSDEN FACTORY Southern Company Invades Birmingham and Other Larger FieldsProduc tion to Be Increased Gadsden Marrh 3SpecialThe Southern Manufacturing company now running nine hours a day and planning on a 10hour shift within a short time j is another concern in the Gadsden dis trict which sees a brightening of the business outlook and a relaxation of the tension of the past few months The local concern has recently se cured some big orders notably one for j a school building at Powderly where they will furnish two or three carloads of doors sashes and other equipments 1 Another carload of finished goods will leave for Jasper this week and other shipments for points in and out of Hhe state are being invoiced Two feeks ago they opened an of I fice in Birmingham which is under the direction of H L Gwinn and Is located at 314 Twentyfirst street There is considerable activity in the building trades in and around Birmingham and some big jobs are contemplated which the local people plan on securing fancy orders The Birmingham venture will be fol lowed by the establishment of offices in Atlanta and with those two central 1 offices they expect"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2022-09-26T03:53:26.109Z", "group": ["ndnp/au", "university-of-alabama-tuscaloosa-al-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn85038485/1921-03-04/ed-1/?sp=7", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:au:batch_au_dean_ver01:data:sn85038485:00340583024:1921030401:0057/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=437&w=310", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:au:batch_au_dean_ver01:data:sn85038485:00340583024:1921030401:0057/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=875&w=621", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/au/batch_au_dean_ver01/data/sn85038485/00340583024/1921030401/0057.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["birmingham", "alabama", "united states",